{"title":"树（王康宁）","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"url":"http://www.tsinsen.com/A1486","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div id=\"pcont1\" style=\"margin-top:20px; display:block;\">\n"},{"title":"# 问题描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　给出一棵N个点的树，每个点有各自的权值，小A想选出一条简单路径，使得这条路径上的点的权值的异或和最大。另外，小A有一些喜欢的点，他希望在这条路径上经过至少K个自己喜欢的点。</div>"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　第一行包括两个整数N, K，分别表示树的点数和路径上至少包含的小A喜欢的点的数量。<br/>\n　　接下来一行N个整数，每个数均为0或1，小A喜欢第i个点当且仅当这一行的第i个数是1。<br/>\n　　接下来一行N个整数V<sub>1</sub>, V<sub>2</sub>, …, V<sub>N</sub>，其中第i个数表示第i个点的权值。<br/>\n　　最后N-1行，每行两个整数u, v，表示树的一条边。</div>"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　如果不存在这样的简单路径，输出-1。否则输出最大的异或和。</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">3 1<br/>\n1 1 1<br/>\n0 4 7<br/>\n1 2<br/>\n2 3</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">7</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">3 2<br/>\n1 0 1<br/>\n3 5 6<br/>\n1 2<br/>\n2 3</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">0</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">4 4<br/>\n1 1 1 1<br/>\n10 10 10 10<br/>\n1 2<br/>\n1 3<br/>\n1 4</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">-1</div>"},{"title":"# 数据规模和约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2px\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\" class=\"table table-striped table-horver\"><tbody><tr style=\"border:solid 1.0pt\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid 1.0pt\">测试点标号<br/>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid 1.0pt\">N的范围<br/>\n</td><td valig